    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this car\u2014it\u2019s an absolute gem and has been my pride and joy. It\u2019s in truly flawless shape, looking and driving just like it did the day it left the showroom. I\u2019ve babied this thing since day one, keeping it spotless and strictly following every service interval. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a great home.",
